• Case 003 – The application for medical aid is currently under review by the provider. We'll share any decisions or requests for additional information as soon as we receive them.

Please let me know if you have any questions or if there's anything else I can do to support our collaboration.

Thank you for your continued partnership.

Best regards,
Jane
Community Health Advocates
